66
00:03:35,940 --> 00:03:38,610
She keeps saying that she heard.

67
00:03:39,570 --> 00:03:41,910
I did!

68
00:03:41,910 --> 00:03:44,940
She's never done it,
but she keeps hearing about it.

69
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:49,100
She's one of the kids herself.
"Kids these days..."

70
00:03:49,140 --> 00:03:52,520
"That's what I hear. I don't,
but they apparently do."

71
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:55,120
That's what I hear. You're right.

72
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,510
You're famously a dating show fanatic.

73
00:03:57,510 --> 00:04:01,770
