74
00:04:01,770 --> 00:04:03,840
Really?

75
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,940
Singing or watching a dating show.

76
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:09,110
My favorite is when people first meet,

77
00:04:09,110 --> 00:04:11,410
