83
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:32,180
When the arrows disconnect like this.

84
00:04:32,180 --> 00:04:35,650
Don't think all the viewers
think a messy show is fun.

85
00:04:35,650 --> 00:04:40,000
I think about these people all week long.

86
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:43,070
- It's fun to watch you like that, too.
- He gets so angry, too.

87
00:04:43,070 --> 00:04:44,770
You just can't do that.

88
00:04:44,770 --> 00:04:49,000
