102
00:05:56,900 --> 00:06:00,000
-I know. He's handsome.
- He's like a model.

103
00:06:03,590 --> 00:06:07,070
- So nice.
- It's so nice.

104
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:10,940
[The warm and elegant fifth Signal House]

105
