move in and buy clothes."

116
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,920
So cute.

117
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:03,010
Could I meet someone nice?

118
00:07:03,010 --> 00:07:06,520
What if I meet my other half

119
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:09,370
