154
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:28,590
Someone who's kind of cute, kind of potato-like.

155
00:09:28,590 --> 00:09:31,850
I've liked men like that.

156
00:09:31,850 --> 00:09:34,480
But he's too handsome.

157
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:38,290
His face is so pale and pretty.

158
00:09:38,300 --> 00:09:43,100
Well, I felt small...

159
00:09:43,100 --> 00:09:47,000
- Wu Yeol seems like a celebrity.
- Yes, I agree.

160
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:51,460
Can I ask how tall you are?

161
00:09:51,460 --> 00:09:54,220
My height? I'm 169 cm.

162
00:09:54,220 --> 00:09:56,560
- She's tall.
- You're tall.

163
00:09:56,560 --> 00:09:58,950
How tall are you? You looked very tall.

164
00:09:58,950 --> 00:10:00,330
I'm 188 cm.

165
00:10:00,330 --> 00:10:02,980
