167
00:10:05,430 --> 00:10:07,090
You're right.

168
00:10:07,090 --> 00:10:08,870
You're so angry, Roy.

169
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:11,070
I don't ask that.

170
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,700
I'm 188 cm.

171
00:10:13,700 --> 00:10:15,630
[Shocked]

172
00:10:18,180 --> 00:10:21,560
