173
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:24,370
I have to go on dates and flirt with him?

174
00:10:24,370 --> 00:10:30,120
I was feeling a bit, "This is too much."

175
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:32,210
So cute.

176
00:10:38,250 --> 00:10:42,250
Do you have a way to relax when you're nervous?

177
00:10:42,250 --> 00:10:44,110
I...

178
00:10:45,900 --> 00:10:48,900
- can't control myself.
- Really?

179
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:52,380
When I'm too nervous, I...

180
00:10:52,380 --> 00:10:55,410
