- No.

182
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:02,900
I like how he talks. "Can you tell?"

183
00:11:04,290 --> 00:11:06,630
How do you relax?

184
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:13,300
I don't have a method, either.
So, I just have to endure it.

185
00:11:13,330 --> 00:11:14,810
Right.

186
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,520
You have to.

187
00:11:19,500 --> 00:11:23,620
[Episode 1: First emotion - Excitement or anxiety]

188
00:11:25,620 --> 00:11:27,770
[Heading to Signal House]

189
00:11:27,770 --> 00:11:29,980
Who's she? She's so...

190
00:11:38,930 --> 00:11:41,390
Happy New Year. Yes.

191
00:11:41,390 --> 00:11:42,830
Thank you.

192
00:11:42,830 --> 00:11:44,530
[Jeong Gyu Ri]

193
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:51,190
[Struggling]

194
00:11:52,900 --> 00:11:56,000
- Someone's here.
- So cute.

195
00:11:58,650 --> 00:12:00,070
[Peeping]

196
00:12:00,070 --> 00:12:01,990
So pretty.

197
00:12:01,990 --> 00:12:04,410
Hello.

198
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:08,000
