199
00:12:12,930 --> 00:12:15,010
Hello.

200
00:12:15,010 --> 00:12:16,270
[Glancing]

201
00:12:21,190 --> 00:12:24,910
Where did you guys put your suitcases?

202
00:12:25,990 --> 00:12:28,700
Hand it to me. I'll carry it for you.

203
00:12:28,700 --> 00:12:30,870
I can wear these, right?

204
00:12:30,870 --> 00:12:32,530
Which one?

205
00:12:32,530 --> 00:12:34,230
It's okay. Just one second.

206
00:12:34,230 --> 00:12:36,450
- So nervous.
- Gosh.

207
00:12:36,450 --> 00:12:37,950
Here.

208
00:12:37,950 --> 00:12:39,910
[Wu Yeol is helping quietly]

209
00:12:39,910 --> 00:12:42,270
Okay. Thank you.

210
00:12:43,110 --> 00:12:44,880
Hello.

211
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:50,060
- So pretty.
- Wow.

212
00:12:56,750 --> 00:12:58,480
Thank you.

213
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,250
Did you already look around?

214
00:13:00,250 --> 00:13:03,920
We only checked out the first floor.

215
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:11,340
[Not even sure where to sit]

216
00:13:15,250 --> 00:13:17,650
Should I sit here?

217
00:13:20,660 --> 00:13:23,200
I'll let you relax.

218
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:26,500
- Wu Yeol must be making her nervous, too.
- Of course.

219
00:13:26,560 --> 00:13:29,420
[The atmosphere slightly changed]

220
00:13:39,970 --> 00:13:41,980
They aren't sure what to do.

221
00:13:41,980 --> 00:13:43,040
[Glancing]

222
00:13:55,460 --> 00:14:00,120
She's so skinny and has a tiny face.

223
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:03,620
A woman in her early 20s came in.

224
00:14:03,620 --> 00:14:06,610
I thought she was a college student.

225
00:14:06,610 --> 00:14:09,310
She's so pretty, and she seemed nice, too.

226
00:14:09,310 --> 00:14:12,170
Are you just putting coats here?

227
00:14:12,170 --> 00:14:13,160
- Yes.
- Yes.

228
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:15,830
You can just put it next to you.

229
00:14:17,070 --> 00:14:18,430
Okay. Got it.

230
00:14:18,430 --> 00:14:21,900
It's nerve-racking to take
your coat off in that situation.

231
00:14:21,900 --> 00:14:23,530
I know.

232
00:14:23,530 --> 00:14:25,980
[Looking around]

233
00:14:31,590 --> 00:14:33,980
What's your name?

234
00:14:34,850 --> 00:14:37,370
I'm Jeong Gyu Ri.

235
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:39,790
Gyu Ri. Nice to meet you.

236
00:14:39,790 --> 00:14:42,020
His ears are red.

237
00:14:42,020 --> 00:14:43,920
I'm Kim Min Ju.

238
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:45,530
Min Ju.

239
00:14:45,530 --> 00:14:47,400
I'm Park Wu Yeol.

240
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:50,440
Park Wu Yeol? Yeol or Ryeol?

241
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,480
Wu Yeol.

242
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:52,970
- Yeol?
- Yes, Yeol.

243
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:56,300
